<h1>South Calgary Real Estate - Marda Loop</h1>
<p>South Calgary forms the southern most section of Marda Loop. Nestled between <a href="/altadore.php">Altadore</a> and <a href="/bankview.php">Bankview</a>, <strong>South Calgary real estate is coveted for its prestigous housing, and lovely tree lined streets</strong>. Many South Calgary homes sit on top the hillside, with beautifull city views and an almost California feel.</p>
